WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.010 --> 00:00:03.060 
In a distant country, there was a young
man named David.

2
00:00:03.710 --> 00:00:08.560 
He had always wanted to learn English,
believing it would open doors to a better future.

3
00:00:09.390 --> 00:00:14.060 
However, David faced a problem, his
father wanted him to work in the family

4
00:00:14.070 --> 00:00:16.260 
bakery instead of pursuing his dreams.

5
00:00:17.230 --> 00:00:19.680 
David's father, an oldest son himself,

6
00:00:19.970 --> 00:00:23.720 
had spent years building their business
and could not understand why his son

7
00:00:23.730 --> 00:00:24.580 
would want to leave.

8
00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:27.960 
One evening, after a long day of working,

9
00:00:28.330 --> 00:00:32.340 
David sat at the kitchen table, feeling
the weight of his father's expectations

10
00:00:32.350 --> 00:00:33.320 
on his shoulders.

11
00:00:34.110 --> 00:00:36.580 
Why can't you understand, he pleaded.

12
00:00:37.130 --> 00:00:41.400 
I want to explore the world and
communicate with people from different cultures.

13
00:00:42.050 --> 00:00:45.180 
His father sighed, you have everything
you need here.

14
00:00:45.790 --> 00:00:47.140 
Why risk it all?

15
00:00:47.990 --> 00:00:50.360 
Determined to follow his dreams, David

16
00:00:50.370 --> 00:00:52.760 
decided to take matters into his own hands.

17
00:00:53.610 --> 00:00:55.880 
He began studying English in secret,

18
00:00:56.210 --> 00:00:59.160 
using books and online resources he had found.

19
00:00:59.170 --> 00:01:02.220 
He spent every spare moment learning new

20
00:01:02.230 --> 00:01:04.020 
words and practicing pronunciation.

21
00:01:04.830 --> 00:01:07.700 
As time went on, he felt more confident

22
00:01:07.710 --> 00:01:09.320 
and excited about the future.

23
00:01:10.010 --> 00:01:13.060 
One day, David received an invitation to

24
00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:15.000 
a language exchange event in the city.

25
00:01:15.550 --> 00:01:18.000 
It was a chance to meet native speakers

26
00:01:18.010 --> 00:01:19.620 
and practice what he had learned.

27
00:01:20.190 --> 00:01:22.100 
He knew this was his moment.

28
00:01:22.670 --> 00:01:27.240 
With a mix of excitement and fear, he
told his father about the opportunity.

29
00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:31.660 
To his surprise, his father reacted
differently than expected.

30
00:01:32.290 --> 00:01:35.500 
If you really want this, he said, then go.

31
00:01:36.190 --> 00:01:39.020 
At the event, David met Valeria, a

32
00:01:39.030 --> 00:01:41.520 
vibrant woman who shared his passion for languages.

33
00:01:42.250 --> 00:01:44.520 
They spent hours talking about their

34
00:01:44.530 --> 00:01:45.940 
dreams and aspirations.

35
00:01:47.090 --> 00:01:49.120 
Valeria encouraged him to continue

36
00:01:49.130 --> 00:01:51.320 
learning and even offered to help him practice.

37
00:01:52.110 --> 00:01:54.860 
As they talked, David realized that this

38
00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:58.660 
connection was more than just about
language, it was about understanding each

39
00:01:58.670 --> 00:01:59.380 
other's worlds.

40
00:02:00.210 --> 00:02:02.560 
However, just as things were looking up,

41
00:02:02.870 --> 00:02:05.360 
David received news that his father had
fallen ill.

42
00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:11.000 
He rushed back home, feeling torn between
his responsibilities and his dreams.

43
00:02:11.670 --> 00:02:16.920 
When he arrived, he found his father weak
but still proud of what David had achieved.

44
00:02:17.570 --> 00:02:21.260 
You've become a man, his father said with
tears in his eyes.

45
00:02:21.830 --> 00:02:24.400 
I see now that your dreams are worthy.

46
00:02:25.010 --> 00:02:27.460 
This moment changed everything for David,

47
00:02:27.730 --> 00:02:32.060 
he understood that pursuing one's passion
could lead to growth not just for himself

48
00:02:32.070 --> 00:02:33.760 
but also for those around him.

49
00:02:34.310 --> 00:02:36.800 
In the end, David continued learning

50
00:02:36.810 --> 00:02:40.420 
English with Valeria's help while also
supporting his father's bakery.

51
00:02:40.430 --> 00:02:45.200 
Their bond grew stronger as they
celebrated both their successes together,

52
00:02:45.590 --> 00:02:48.520 
a true testament to the power of love and understanding.

